            },
            {
                "comment": "Really funny guy and a generally good teacher, but sometimes the content and grading schemes don't line up well with what's on the tests, which makes for a confusing class. If you do your homework, the class isn't too bad.",
                "difficulty_rating": 2,
                "quality_rating": 3
            },
            {
                "comment": "If given the chance, I wouldn't have wanted to take this course with another professor. Dr. Block is tough but fair and you have a lot of chances (tests, quizzes, labs, homeworks, etc.) to get good grades. Tests were open bookopen note so it's important to go to class and get the notes.",
